Railway guards stage demo for pay matrixMembers of All India Guards Council (AIGC) staged a demonstration in front of the Divisional Railway Managerâ€™s office here on Monday demanding enhanced revised pay matrix for goods guards, special running allowance, a hike in dress allowance, payment of kilometre allowance as per the Bhalla committee recommendations with effect from January 1, 2006 and payment of annual increment at the rate of five per cent. AIGC Vijayawada Divisional president Patruduwas among those present.